This paper is about improving the performance of reinforcement learning-based document summarization systems by learning a better reward function. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and machine learning. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE), which are also relevant sub-categories.
